1
00:00:36,704 --> 00:00:39,424
=Love Behind the Mask=

2
00:00:39,648 --> 00:00:41,312
=Episode 29=

3
00:00:41,696 --> 00:00:42,688
♪Is it♪

4
00:00:42,880 --> 00:00:44,000
Why did you fall asleep?

5
00:00:45,159 --> 00:00:45,719
Shu.

6
00:00:46,880 --> 00:00:48,128
♪Trap♪

7
00:00:48,640 --> 00:00:50,240
♪I can't get over it♪

8
00:00:52,079 --> 00:00:53,119
What's wrong?

9
00:00:56,256 --> 00:00:57,984
♪We♪

10
00:00:59,399 --> 00:01:00,000
I'm sorry.

11
00:01:01,960 --> 00:01:02,600
I suddenly

12
00:01:03,479 --> 00:01:04,879
remembered something in the past.

13
00:01:06,799 --> 00:01:07,456
Come.

14
00:01:07,719 --> 00:01:08,288
Sit.

15
00:01:11,008 --> 00:01:14,240
♪It turns out nothing has changed♪

16
00:01:14,624 --> 00:01:18,240
♪Just pretend the story is replaying♪

17
00:01:18,624 --> 00:01:21,152
♪If I see you again♪

18
00:01:22,000 --> 00:01:23,680
I often come here with an old friend

19
00:01:24,920 --> 00:01:26,120
to watch fireflies.

20
00:01:26,304 --> 00:01:27,744
♪You are♪

21
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,239
I'm tired.

22
00:01:33,079 --> 00:01:34,519
Can I lean on you for a bit?

23
00:01:35,424 --> 00:01:38,912
♪To pretend not to see you♪

24
00:01:40,160 --> 00:01:42,432
♪Why do we♪

25
00:01:42,432 --> 00:01:44,640
♪Dare not continue to write♪

26
00:01:44,640 --> 00:01:47,584
♪At the same time♪

27
00:01:47,808 --> 00:01:49,792
♪Do I have to♪

28
00:01:49,920 --> 00:01:53,600
♪Forget you again♪

29
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:04,799
Wangyou.

30
00:02:09,639 --> 00:02:10,879
There's no news about her yet.

31
00:02:12,240 --> 00:02:13,520
If she didn't want to leave,

32
00:02:14,039 --> 00:02:15,319
no one could take her away.

33
00:02:15,759 --> 00:02:16,360
Jiyao,

34
00:02:17,159 --> 00:02:17,840
do you think

35
00:02:18,800 --> 00:02:19,919
it's my fault?

36
00:02:25,639 --> 00:02:26,479
I don't know.

37
00:02:27,599 --> 00:02:28,240
But I think

38
00:02:29,280 --> 00:02:30,319
love is not possession

39
00:02:31,759 --> 00:02:32,759
but letting go.

40
00:02:34,280 --> 00:02:35,159
Letting go?

41
00:02:36,479 --> 00:02:37,960
How am I supposed to let her go?

42
00:02:38,960 --> 00:02:40,919
The thought of her
being with someone else

43
00:02:41,080 --> 00:02:42,479
drives me mad.

44
00:02:43,520 --> 00:02:44,520
Yan Shi'an,

45
00:02:44,960 --> 00:02:46,280
wake up, will you?

46
00:02:47,199 --> 00:02:48,879
You're surrounded by enemies.

47
00:02:49,520 --> 00:02:51,879
Everyone is eyeing your throne greedily.

48
00:02:53,159 --> 00:02:54,439
Don't you know that?

49
00:02:55,719 --> 00:02:57,120
Driving you mad?

50
00:02:58,280 --> 00:02:59,759
You're the heir to the throne.

51
00:03:00,039 --> 00:03:01,879
Don't indulge yourself
in personal affections.

52
00:03:02,319 --> 00:03:03,360
The throne?

53
00:03:04,319 --> 00:03:05,000
Crown Prince?

54
00:03:05,080 --> 00:03:05,879
Heir?

55
00:03:07,159 --> 00:03:08,319
If I had a choice,

56
00:03:08,479 --> 00:03:09,759
I wouldn't want to be them.

57
00:03:10,479 --> 00:03:11,840
I just want to be with Anning

58
00:03:11,960 --> 00:03:13,280
and go back to those mountains.

59
00:03:14,479 --> 00:03:15,639
What did I do wrong?

60
00:03:16,639 --> 00:03:17,639
I did nothing wrong.

61
00:03:35,039 --> 00:03:35,719
Your Highness.

62
00:04:02,360 --> 00:04:03,520
Don't come here anymore.

63
00:04:06,759 --> 00:04:07,560
Your Highness,

64
00:04:09,960 --> 00:04:11,800
did I do something wrong?

65
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:16,920
I have a more important task for you.

66
00:04:18,279 --> 00:04:19,199
(Si Yichen,)

67
00:04:19,959 --> 00:04:21,759
(I am looking forward to your reaction.)

68
00:04:22,176 --> 00:04:26,304
(Princess Royal's Mansion)

69
00:04:29,680 --> 00:04:30,319
We've arrived.

70
00:04:30,560 --> 00:04:31,720
Princess Royal's Mansion?

71
00:04:32,279 --> 00:04:33,319
Is this your home?

72
00:04:34,480 --> 00:04:36,120
It's the home of my friend.

73
00:04:37,480 --> 00:04:38,199
Let's get inside.

74
00:04:39,488 --> 00:04:41,600
♪The night becomes sleepless♪

75
00:04:42,080 --> 00:04:46,656
♪I'm left behind in the world alone♪

76
00:04:47,079 --> 00:04:48,439
Your home is so beautiful.

77
00:04:48,576 --> 00:04:50,240
♪Through all the love♪

78
00:04:50,240 --> 00:04:52,736
♪And hatred♪

79
00:04:53,319 --> 00:04:54,680
You won't trap me here

80
00:04:54,959 --> 00:04:55,959
like Shi'an did

81
00:04:56,240 --> 00:04:57,959
and allow me to see no one, right?

82
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:00,120
Stay here

83
00:05:00,439 --> 00:05:01,519
for the time being.

84
00:05:01,879 --> 00:05:03,079
When I find out the truth,

85
00:05:03,639 --> 00:05:05,000
you can walk free.

86
00:05:05,480 --> 00:05:06,240
The truth?

87
00:05:06,600 --> 00:05:07,480
What do you mean?

88
00:05:08,600 --> 00:05:09,879
You want to see Tiandu's beauty?

89
00:05:10,784 --> 00:05:14,016
♪We are fated, yet not deeply enough♪

90
00:05:14,016 --> 00:05:16,448
♪We own each other nothing♪

91
00:05:18,000 --> 00:05:19,600
Come and take a look.

92
00:05:20,864 --> 00:05:21,888
♪That was sundered into halves♪

93
00:05:21,888 --> 00:05:24,704
♪When love cannot reconnect♪

94
00:05:25,079 --> 00:05:26,480
The view is so beautiful.

95
00:05:26,839 --> 00:05:28,160
I will remember it well.

96
00:05:28,439 --> 00:05:29,920
You do look like someone

97
00:05:30,240 --> 00:05:31,519
who has never seen the world.

98
00:05:33,399 --> 00:05:34,360
It's said

99
00:05:34,480 --> 00:05:35,879
I've been sickly since childhood

100
00:05:36,120 --> 00:05:37,240
and raised in the palace.

101
00:05:37,560 --> 00:05:38,920
Shi'an rarely let me go out.

102
00:05:39,680 --> 00:05:40,839
So I have never seen

103
00:05:41,199 --> 00:05:42,680
such a view before.

104
00:05:45,439 --> 00:05:47,439
Have we truly never seen each other?

105
00:05:47,920 --> 00:05:49,319
Don't you remember me?

106
00:05:50,680 --> 00:05:51,232
No.

107
00:05:51,560 --> 00:05:54,160
Why do your eyes look so sad?

108
00:05:55,160 --> 00:05:56,639
It seems you're seeing someone else

109
00:05:57,680 --> 00:05:59,040
through me.

110
00:05:59,232 --> 00:06:01,504
♪And hatred♪

111
00:06:01,504 --> 00:06:06,752
♪I can't escape destiny's scheme♪

112
00:06:07,264 --> 00:06:09,664
♪With one glance♪

113
00:06:10,048 --> 00:06:12,352
♪The bond resolves♪

114
00:06:12,768 --> 00:06:17,792
♪Let me wait another ten thousand years♪

115
00:06:18,080 --> 00:06:21,568
♪We are fated, yet not deeply enough♪

116
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,600
Yanshu?

117
00:06:41,519 --> 00:06:42,199
What happened

118
00:06:42,639 --> 00:06:43,879
just now?

119
00:06:44,639 --> 00:06:45,519
I suddenly

120
00:06:46,199 --> 00:06:47,160
got a headache.

121
00:06:47,720 --> 00:06:48,920
I can't remember clearly.

122
00:06:49,319 --> 00:06:50,639
Then rest well first.

123
00:06:52,600 --> 00:06:53,279
Mu Han,

124
00:06:53,920 --> 00:06:56,160
can you stay?

125
00:06:59,199 --> 00:06:59,759
Okay.

126
00:07:00,680 --> 00:07:01,519
I'm here.

127
00:07:01,959 --> 00:07:02,519
Sleep now.

128
00:07:09,199 --> 00:07:09,920
Miss Wangyou's

129
00:07:10,279 --> 00:07:11,519
temperament is completely

130
00:07:11,959 --> 00:07:13,199
different from Wen Yanshu's.

131
00:07:13,759 --> 00:07:15,759
I have not had much contact with them.

132
00:07:16,120 --> 00:07:16,639
But

133
00:07:16,839 --> 00:07:17,720
it's obvious.

134
00:07:17,959 --> 00:07:18,839
(Prosperity Court)
No matter what,

135
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:21,319
in my heart,

136
00:07:22,120 --> 00:07:23,399
she's always Wen Yanshu.

137
00:07:23,959 --> 00:07:24,680
But

138
00:07:25,600 --> 00:07:26,519
could it be

139
00:07:26,680 --> 00:07:28,319
that Miss Wangyou
is pretending all this?

140
00:07:30,920 --> 00:07:31,839
Pretending?

141
00:07:32,120 --> 00:07:32,720
How about

142
00:07:33,120 --> 00:07:33,959
we test her again?

143
00:07:37,959 --> 00:07:38,759
Yanshu,

144
00:07:40,920 --> 00:07:42,680
why won't you acknowledge me?

145
00:07:51,720 --> 00:07:52,920
It's nice tonight.

146
00:07:53,839 --> 00:07:54,800
Join me for a drink.

147
00:07:56,480 --> 00:07:57,024
Okay.

148
00:07:59,079 --> 00:08:00,600
I want to thank you

149
00:08:00,800 --> 00:08:01,680
for what you did.

150
00:08:16,120 --> 00:08:16,920
Did you

151
00:08:17,439 --> 00:08:18,519
prepare all these dishes?

152
00:08:18,680 --> 00:08:19,296
Yes.

153
00:08:19,680 --> 00:08:21,319
They're the cuisine of my hometown.

154
00:08:21,879 --> 00:08:23,079
I once had a friend

155
00:08:23,639 --> 00:08:24,519
who liked it a lot.

156
00:08:25,079 --> 00:08:26,360
I think you will like it too.

157
00:08:40,960 --> 00:08:41,480
How is it?

158
00:08:41,759 --> 00:08:42,480
It's tasty.

159
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:44,240
That friend of yours

160
00:08:44,519 --> 00:08:45,639
must be very happy.

161
00:08:47,480 --> 00:08:48,600
Let's have another drink.

162
00:08:49,679 --> 00:08:50,200
Come on.

163
00:08:50,519 --> 00:08:51,200
Okay.

164
00:08:59,960 --> 00:09:01,039
You've been at my mansion

165
00:09:01,320 --> 00:09:02,519
for many days.

166
00:09:06,279 --> 00:09:07,480
How will you repay me?

167
00:09:08,159 --> 00:09:09,080
Then I will

168
00:09:09,480 --> 00:09:10,879
toast you again.

169
00:09:11,679 --> 00:09:12,360
Come on.

170
00:09:29,000 --> 00:09:30,519
I have a question for you.

171
00:09:31,279 --> 00:09:32,159
Yes?

172
00:09:33,480 --> 00:09:34,360
Are you sure

173
00:09:34,799 --> 00:09:36,200
you don't remember me?

174
00:09:36,960 --> 00:09:38,879
Why are you asking that again?

175
00:09:39,039 --> 00:09:40,320
I really don't remember you.

176
00:09:40,559 --> 00:09:41,679
I haven't seen you before.

177
00:09:43,519 --> 00:09:44,240
But

178
00:09:47,519 --> 00:09:49,279
every time I see you,

179
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:50,720
it feels

180
00:09:51,360 --> 00:09:53,799
very different here.

181
00:10:21,856 --> 00:10:25,184
♪It's hard to part♪

182
00:10:25,408 --> 00:10:28,320
♪The loneliness in heart♪

183
00:10:28,960 --> 00:10:31,648
♪Weighing right and wrong♪

184
00:10:32,128 --> 00:10:34,976
♪The regret is beyond speech♪

185
00:10:35,968 --> 00:10:39,328
♪The cloud river gleams♪

186
00:10:39,680 --> 00:10:42,080
♪What is a touch of love♪

187
00:10:42,784 --> 00:10:46,240
♪Lowering eyes tenderly,
scattered glances♪

188
00:10:46,240 --> 00:10:50,784
♪Capturing the sad union♪

189
00:10:50,784 --> 00:10:55,136
♪Even if the chaotic world
is like stardust♪

190
00:10:55,136 --> 00:10:58,336
♪Residing between your brows and eyes♪

191
00:10:58,336 --> 00:11:02,400
♪Suddenly a drop of regret is lifted♪

192
00:11:02,400 --> 00:11:05,280
♪Melting the snow on my shoulders♪

193
00:11:06,039 --> 00:11:06,879
Mu Han?

194
00:11:09,536 --> 00:11:12,448
♪Holding a falling petal♪

195
00:11:12,448 --> 00:11:14,592
♪Not in vain
is this predestined calamity♪

196
00:11:19,584 --> 00:11:21,344
(Princess Royal's Mansion)

197
00:11:22,960 --> 00:11:23,679
My lord.

198
00:11:24,399 --> 00:11:25,279
The wine you sent...

199
00:11:26,080 --> 00:11:27,120
It worked well, right?

200
00:11:27,519 --> 00:11:28,879
Did she recall the past...?

201
00:11:29,120 --> 00:11:30,039
No pay for this month.

202
00:11:30,799 --> 00:11:31,799
By the way,

203
00:11:32,039 --> 00:11:32,840
