205
00:12:07,039 --> 00:12:08,440
(Birthday Paper)
Mu Han's birthday?

206
00:12:09,480 --> 00:12:10,919
Isn't it tomorrow?

207
00:12:27,399 --> 00:12:30,279
Why does she look exactly like me?

208
00:12:35,120 --> 00:12:36,080
Could it be

209
00:12:36,919 --> 00:12:38,200
that he likes me?

210
00:12:42,440 --> 00:12:43,519
I'll wait for him.

211
00:12:57,120 --> 00:12:58,888
♪In the deserted world♪

212
00:12:59,110 --> 00:13:00,639
♪There are countless thoughts♪

213
00:13:01,142 --> 00:13:03,689
♪How many of them come true♪

214
00:13:05,065 --> 00:13:06,433
♪I've asked a thousand times♪

215
00:13:06,707 --> 00:13:08,493
♪Who is writing♪

216
00:13:09,064 --> 00:13:12,317
♪Our mutual wishes♪

217
00:13:12,676 --> 00:13:14,346
♪When I open my eyes♪

218
00:13:14,527 --> 00:13:16,373
♪I see your smiling face♪

219
00:13:16,526 --> 00:13:19,988
♪Years pass by like fleeting water♪

220
00:13:20,483 --> 00:13:22,145
♪And the world keeps changing♪

221
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:28,960
♪I wish to be with you
for the rest of my life♪

222
00:13:29,504 --> 00:13:31,929
♪No fear of winds far away♪

223
00:13:32,100 --> 00:13:33,839
♪Between you and me♪

224
00:13:33,990 --> 00:13:37,751
♪Time is exchanged for moments♪

225
00:13:37,926 --> 00:13:39,433
♪If wishes can come true♪

226
00:13:39,594 --> 00:13:41,533
